      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, i get the \"extremes\" part, but isn't it kind of a stretch to say it's \"necessary\" for a society to function? it feels like you're saying it's a good thing by default. can't you have social cohesion through just shared values or something without the whole \"nationalism\" baggage?",
